STAR - CROSSED ( TV SERIES )
Star - Crossed is an American science fiction romantic teen drama television series created by Meredith Averill .
Star - Crossed premiered on The CW on February 17 , 2014 .
On May 8 , 2014 , The CW cancelled Star - Crossed after one season .
SYNOPSIS
Section::::Synopsis .
Set in the near - future in 2024 , the series follows a romance between a human girl named Emery and an alien boy named Roman when he and six others of his kind are integrated into a suburban high school .
It is filmed and takes place in Louisiana in the fictional town of Edendale .
