BROADCAST Section::::Broadcast .
The series aired in Australia , eight and a half hours behind the East Coast of the United States on Fox8 from Tuesday , February 18 , 2014 , at 8:30 p.m.
In the United Kingdom , the show aired on Sky 1 on Friday , April 4 , 2014 at 8 p.m. REFERENCES EXTERNAL LINKS